level 0
keywords help
---
Syntax: help [topic]

Displays help information on a given topic. Without arguments, shows the
summary help page. Topics include command names, skills, races, classes,
and game concepts.

Related commands:
  shelp  - Help on skills and spells (detailed staff reference)
  rhelp  - Help on races
  sthelp - Help on stances
  rmlist - List racial modifiers
